{"tid":1555163,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"羅范椒芬打抹黑牌，證明政府對抗爭者已經無計可施","createTime":"2019-09-09T09:01:06.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-09T09:18:21.000Z","uid":146454,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"cbf73c11461fc50c0ca90017ac5f6951731f9313","tid":1555163,"uid":146454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T09:01:06.000Z","msg":"作為一個行政會議成員，佢需要保皇奶共無可厚非。但係佢唔用道理攻擊示威者，而係選擇用流言裴語做人格謀殺，<strong>除咗證明呢個政府好低莊之外，佢哋似乎已經無理據去說服啲人放棄抗爭，或者逆轉民意。</strong><br />\n<br />\n一個人發言，候除咗留意佢講咩，亦都要留意佢想爭取咩人支持。呢一種嘅攻擊方法，<strong>只會對一啲唔擅長fact check，教育程度低嘅人受落</strong>。政府得返呢一班人做基本盤，其實好悲哀。<br />\n<br />\n所有如果你地屋企人傾起呢件事，你唔需要同佢哋爭論係咪真有其事。直接同佢講，因為呢啲所謂嘅事實就否定示威者嘅訴求，係人都笑你冇腦啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d2925c02a932bc61663bfd707199f0b4f8462b33","tid":1555163,"uid":146454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T09:01:35.000Z","msg":"1/10"},{"pid":"ba1d96aa9af2f677abde18ff384e701d03a8a74a","tid":1555163,"uid":146454,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T09:01:45.000Z","msg":"2/10"},{"pid":"d8188a8c1d9e591e0ff34a280374e2095ec68fad","tid":1555163,"uid":146454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T09:01:55.000Z","msg":"3/10"},{"pid":"d557bcfd61471d8419606224a787655ee1a9ad71","tid":1555163,"uid":146454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T09:02:05.000Z","msg":"4/10"},{"pid":"66940ebce09d2c8ee6b1c9620d5b80a8e924e93c","tid":1555163,"uid":146454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T09:02:26.000Z","msg":"五大訴求 缺一不可"},{"pid":"de9036a22dc11c868d56e50cca8992c7a1acb603","tid":1555163,"uid":54785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T09:02:36.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e1fa14232f52bbb524f7067aedec1e3d46c93d34","tid":1555163,"uid":146454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"20